# Golden Dragon Theorem — Repository Specification
### PantheonOS: golden-dragon-theorem/

---

## 1. Purpose

This repository contains reference implementation of the **Golden Dragon Curve** visualizer, data structures for the **Golden Dragon Attractor**, simulation notebooks, and documentation for using the theorem as an engineering design check.

---

## 2. Recommended Structure

```text
golden-dragon-theorem/
├─ README.md
├─ docs/
│  ├─ golden_dragon_theorem_whitepaper.md
│  ├─ golden_dragon_theorem_codex.md
│  └─ diagrams/
│     └─ golden_dragon_curve_ascii.md
├─ src/
│  ├─ gdt_core.py
│  ├─ ethics_module.py
│  ├─ time_trident_adapter.py
│  ├─ story_safe_kernel_adapter.py
│  └─ hogge_attractor_interface.py
├─ examples/
│  ├─ scenario_traces/
│  │  ├─ simple_run.json
│  │  └─ high_stress_run.json
│  └─ notebooks/
│     └─ golden_dragon_visualizer.ipynb
├─ tests/
│  ├─ test_ethics_threshold.py
│  ├─ test_grand_invariant.py
│  ├─ test_time_trident_stability.py
│  └─ test_positive_sum_property.py
└─ config/
   ├─ gdt_defaults.yaml
   └─ ethics_thresholds.yaml
